text: The Mozambique women's national handball team is the national team of Mozambique. It is governed by the Federaçao Moçambicana de Andebol and takes part in international handball competitions. ==African Championship record== *1996 – 6th *1998 – 5th ==External links== *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Handball National team
title: Mozambique women's national handball team
